Description :
        A compilation of oneshots done by various authors 1) Mistress Princess (Shiiku Hime) Takanezawa Hime is girl from a wealthy family. When they were small she started bullying Asakawa Nachi. Under Hime's guidance she wants Nachi to become her ideal pet. And thats why Nachi always obey to Hime's commands. 2) Egoism of Passion (Jyuu Yoku Egoism) Suzu is dating the student council president Hagane. She's always touching him, but since their first time Hagane hasn't tried to hold her. What can she do to spark his interest again?
